                                                        <h3 class="gdlr-core-title-item-title gdlr-core-skin-title " style="font-size: 34px ;font-weight: 700 ;letter-spacing: 0px ;text-transform: none ;color: #161616 ;">Shri Surendra M. Patel</h3></div><span class="gdlr-core-title-item-caption gdlr-core-info-font gdlr-core-skin-caption" style="font-size: 20px ;font-style: normal ;color: #6c6c6c ;">President, CHARUSAT</span></div>
